subject: College Athletics
Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: With Cody Zeller’s help, No. 1 Indiana cruised past No. 14 North Carolina in the A.C.C.-Big Ten Challenge. In other action, No. 3 Michigan and No. 21 Minnesota both won.
